      <hedline>
        <hl1>'Footloose' to Close</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Footloose, Broadway musical, announces closing (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''Footloose,'' a musical based on the 1984 film and adapted by Dean Pitchford and Walter Bobbie, is to close after the matinee on July 2 at the Richard Rodgers Theater, 226 West 46th Street, Manhattan. The show, directed by Mr. Bobbie with music by Tom Snow and lyrics by Mr. Pitchford, will have run for 737 regular performances and 21 previews.</p>
      </block>
